                    "expr": {
                      "Literal": {
                        "Value": "'[{\"textRuns\":[{\"value\":\"This report provides comprehensive sales performance insights for the AdventureWorks reseller channel. The data model follows a medallion architecture (Bronze → Silver → Gold) with a star schema design optimized for Direct Lake analytics on Microsoft Fabric.\\n\\nKey Features:\\n• Sales vs Target tracking with attainment metrics\\n• Profit margin and profitability analysis\\n• Regional performance breakdown\\n• Product and salesperson insights\\n• Interactive drill-down: Region → Product → Salesperson\",\"textStyle\":{\"fontFamily\":\"Segoe UI, wf_segoe-ui_normal, helvetica, arial, sans-serif\",\"fontSize\":\"14px\",\"fontWeight\":\"normal\"}}],\"horizontalAlignment\":\"center\"}]'"
